<% content_for :page_title, "Welcome" %>
<% content_for :nav_key, "dashboard" %>

<div class="space-y-8">
  <div class="card">
    <p class="text-[var(--color-fg-muted)] text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Aşama 0 — Shell</p>
    <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-5xl mt-3 tracking-tight">Hello, Meridian.</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-[var(--color-fg-muted)] max-w-xl">
      Bu, projenin temel iskeletinin canlı görüntüsüdür: Rails 8, Hotwire, Tailwind v4,
      Fraunces + DM Sans tipografi, dark-first palet ve ViewComponent layout şablonu.
      Modüller (Finance, Todos, Habits, Calendar, Journal, Goals) sonraki aşamalarda eklenecek.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
    <div class="card">
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-fg-muted)]">Stack</p>
      <p class="stat-number mt-2">Rails 8</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-fg-faint)] mt-2">Hotwire · Importmap · Propshaft</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-fg-muted)]">Design</p>
      <p class="stat-number mt-2">Fraunces</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-fg-faint)] mt-2">DM Sans body · Amber/gold accent</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-fg-muted)]">Status</p>
      <p class="stat-number mt-2">0/12</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-fg-faint)] mt-2">Aşamalar tamamlandı</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
